HEADWORD: Thoracentesis
<hw>Tho`ra*cen*te"sis</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL.,
fr. Gr. <?/ thorax + <?/ pricking, from <?/ to prick, stab.]</ety>
